299
00:10:58,500 --> 00:11:00,375
there wouldn't be
any baseball on TV,

300
00:11:00,458 --> 00:11:02,125
and I'd get to
watch all my anime.

301
00:11:02,208 --> 00:11:03,458
[TSUKASA]
I should have known

302
00:11:03,541 --> 00:11:05,000
you'd say something like that.

303
00:11:05,083 --> 00:11:06,375
[KONATA]
Yeah, but now they've got

