don't you think?

333
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:56,708
[KAGAMI]
You're right.

334
00:11:56,791 --> 00:11:59,083
I couldn't agree with you more.

335
00:11:59,166 --> 00:12:01,666
And since you brought it up,
Konata, I was always surprised

336
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:03,666
that you got accepted
to this school.

337
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:05,208
