371
00:13:09,375 --> 00:13:10,333
No way.

372
00:13:10,416 --> 00:13:11,625
[chuckles]

373
00:13:11,708 --> 00:13:12,958
[KAGAMI]
Maybe she went and memorized

374
00:13:13,041 --> 00:13:14,583
all the questions and answers.

375
00:13:14,666 --> 00:13:17,958
Her memory's sharp as a tack
when it comes to games!

376
00:13:18,041 --> 00:13:19,458
So what are we
gonna play next?

377
00:13:19,541 --> 00:13:21,416
You in a hurry or something?

378
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:23,333
Hey, that's weird,
where is it?

379
00:13:23,416 --> 00:13:25,000
Didn't you used to
have an easy party game

