390
00:13:38,625 --> 00:13:40,666
Usually, you gobble 'em all up.

391
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:42,291
No reason, I just
don't want any.

392
00:13:42,375 --> 00:13:43,583
Oh, I get it.

393
00:13:43,666 --> 00:13:45,541
You're on a summer
diet, aren't ya?

