397
00:13:50,083 --> 00:13:50,916
Shut up!

398
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:51,916
You don't need to go there!

399
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,166
Oh, that's right.

400
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:54,666
You guys were born
on the Star Festival.

401
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:56,708
It's almost your
birthday, isn't it?

402
00:13:56,791 --> 00:13:57,875
Yeah, so what?

403
00:13:57,958 --> 00:13:59,791
Oh, Kona-chan, you
remembered our birthday!

404
00:13:59,875 --> 00:14:00,708
Mm-hmm.

405
00:14:00,791 --> 00:14:02,000
We're gonna be seventeen.

