448
00:15:21,083 --> 00:15:22,958
Kona-chan, you look great!

449
00:15:23,041 --> 00:15:25,458
I think you totally
pull off that look.

450
00:15:25,541 --> 00:15:26,833
Yeah, you think so?

451
00:15:26,916 --> 00:15:28,666
Mm, I really do.

452
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,750
