481
00:16:21,333 --> 00:16:23,416
[TSUKASA]
Twinkle, twinkle, twinkle.

482
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:24,458
[KONATA]
I'm just hopin' that

483
00:16:24,541 --> 00:16:26,250
your reckless charm works.

484
00:16:26,333 --> 00:16:28,500
[KAGAMI]
