00:16:36,625 --> 00:16:38,333
Hm? Oh, I don't use 'em.

490
00:16:38,416 --> 00:16:40,458
But, why do you
collect them, then?

491
00:16:40,541 --> 00:16:41,916
When something comes out
that's related to

492
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,541
a show or manga you like,

493
00:16:43,625 --> 00:16:46,458
don't you wanna have it,
as a collector and as a fan?

494
00:16:46,541 --> 00:16:48,958
Okay, but you're supposed to
use those things, aren't you?

495
00:16:49,041 --> 00:16:50,416
You can't use them, ever!

496
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,250
You have to store
them someplace safe.

497
00:16:52,333 --> 00:16:54,208
It really pisses me off
when I see all those people

498
00:16:54,291 --> 00:16:56,250
using those cards
like common money.

499
00:16:56,333 --> 00:16:57,666
These are sacred things.

500
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,583
They're meant to be bought
and carefully archived.

501
00:16:59,666 --> 00:17:01,083
You're not supposed to use 'em,

502
00:17:01,166 --> 00:17:02,791
and it's out of the question
to go and auction 'em!

503
00:17:02,875 --> 00:17:06,208
