00:17:12,666 --> 00:17:14,291
First off, I pull
the most pristine one

509
00:17:14,375 --> 00:17:17,041
and lock it away for
eternity in a special case.

510
00:17:17,125 --> 00:17:18,375
The second card's for me to keep

